@model MinsuXize.Web.Models.SubmissionRecord

<section class="page-header">
    <span class="eyebrow">提交成功</span>
    <h1>我们已经收到你的补充</h1>
    <p>这条记录会先进入待核实状态，后续根据来源完整度和内容清晰度整理进词条。</p>
    <div class="meta-list">
        <span>编号：@Model.Id</span>
        <span>标题：@Model.Title</span>
        <span>状态：@Model.Status</span>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="content-section section-panel">
    <h2>下一步</h2>
    <p>如果后续需要补充照片、录音、出处或更明确的地点，可以再次提交并在摘要里标注与本次记录有关。</p>
    <div class="utility-actions">
        <a class="button-primary" asp-controller="Entries" asp-action="Index">浏览词条</a>
        <a class="button-secondary" asp-controller="Submit" asp-action="Create">继续提交</a>
    </div>
</section>
